<section class="infra-flow">
  <div class="container-lg">
    <div class="infra-editorial">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <span class="infra-kicker">How It Works</span>
        <h2 class="infra-title elicyon">A manufacturing flow designed for repeatable quality.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-up" data-delay="140">
        <p class="infra-copy">
          The plant brings core processes closer together, reducing handoffs and helping teams monitor material behavior from film preparation through coating, extrusion, finishing, utilities, and packing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-flow__steps">
      <article class="infra-step fade-up">
        <i class="ti ti-building-factory-2"></i>
        <h3>Film & Base Preparation</h3>
        <p>Calendar systems prepare the core PVC film structure for decorative and interior applications.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="infra-step fade-up" data-delay="100">
        <i class="ti ti-layers-intersect"></i>
        <h3>Lamination & Coating</h3>
        <p>Hot, cold, PE, and silicon coating systems support decorative film and self-adhesive material requirements.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="infra-step fade-up" data-delay="200">
        <i class="ti ti-ruler-measure"></i>
        <h3>Extrusion & Finishing</h3>
        <p>PVC foam board, PVC/WPC wall panel extrusion, rotogravure printing, and PUR wrapping extend the plant into rigid and interior products.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="infra-step fade-up" data-delay="300">
        <i class="ti ti-package"></i>
        <h3>In-House Packing</h3>
        <p>Paper tubes and hard covers are made on-site so finished products remain protected in transit.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

